platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Few things are more relaxing than settling down with a good coloring book—at least, until the kid we borrowed it from asks for it back. Pigment unleashes our grown-up creative energy with a surprisingly deep array of artist’s tools and tweaks. It even lets us automatically color within the lines, giving our productions a sheen of perfection. We expect a call from the gallery any day now.
Best of 2016 次点作品（iPad App 部門）- 紙と画材を使っているかのようにイラストに色を塗っていくことができる塗り絵 App。細密で美しいイラストを11のツールと無数の色の組み合わせで塗り分けることで、癒しと自己表現を可能に。Apple Pencil を使えば画材の質感やタッチがさらにリアルに。

Few things are more relaxing than settling down with a good colouring book—at least, until the kid we borrowed it from asks for it back. Pigment unleashes our grown-up creative energy with a surprisingly deep array of artist’s tools and tweaks. It even lets us automatically colour within the lines, giving our productions a sheen of perfection. We expect a call from the gallery any day now.
